{"tid":231773,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[周圍碌] 東歐巴爾幹半島遊記","createTime":"2017-05-06T09:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T11:11:06.000Z","uid":74041,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ffc5c4b5440c07ca005f8e16a04f40d433c29ab","tid":231773,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:51:53.000Z","msg":"上年用左三個月時間玩歐洲，再搭西伯利亞鐵路經蒙古返香港，成個經歷實在太正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但一次過寫返實在太長，思前想後決定寫返係東歐的經歷出嚟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講起歐洲，相信大家第一時間都會諗起英國，法國，意大利等出名而又高消費的國家，但好想同各位巴絲打講，除左貴到離地的西歐，另一邊的歐洲其實相對親民好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，除左傳統歐洲建築外，亦有好多值得一去的地方。東歐，識玩其實好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於東歐的劃分有唔同講法，我會跟返自己路線嚟打。巴爾幹半島係東歐的一部分，泛指前南斯拉夫分裂成的國家，包括塞爾維亞，黑山，馬其頓等好多香港人聽都未聽過的國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，亦有科索沃這個宣稱獨立但未得到國際廣泛承認的特別存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次的路線如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/emfx1g3u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Femfx1g3u&h=0035c6bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斯洛伐克&gt;匈牙利&gt;奧地利&gt;捷克&gt;波蘭 (中間經波羅的海三小國入左俄仔) ，再去烏克蘭&gt;摩爾多瓦(去埋404既Transnistria)&gt;羅馬尼亞&gt;塞爾維亞&gt;黑山&gt;阿爾巴尼亞&gt;科索沃&gt;馬其頓&gt;保加利亞，然後再入俄仔繼續行程<br />\n<br />\n老實講東歐本身唔係我計劃之內，我志在周圍碌下，有D國家可能只留1晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好多時都係今日先決定聽日去邊，好多景點我都無特別去，算係走馬看花，歡迎指教。<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 都係果句，有時忙起上嚟可能出唔到文，勿追文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee61924d6c4fed9a47b6ade8c1d103762f6135a8","tid":231773,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:52:37.000Z","msg":"fb同步更新: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wanderingaroundtheworld/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwanderingaroundtheworld%2F&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=83796a7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wanderingaroundtheworld/</a>  跪求like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868ee66b8dc4bcbc8b9fc07ed2e956413111e735","tid":231773,"uid":28336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>fb同步更新: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wanderingaroundtheworld/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwanderingaroundtheworld%2F&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=83796a7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wanderingaroundtheworld/</a>  跪求like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返屋企like 遲d想自己一個去東歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0196c2e6dd8a9f50988af9c7b6f7bd83db252ae","tid":231773,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:29:10.000Z","msg":"斯洛伐克去左邊?"},{"pid":"1d20a49ead5942337fa65b4f3b13ed7407a9f505","tid":231773,"uid":64835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T15:12:37.000Z","msg":"文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e3968751644177e84c1fa354ba988860dfeaab","tid":231773,"uid":93947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"點解唔去克羅地亞呀？好正喎"},{"pid":"f5fbc5bbf93e6b2db59b247cf8f01fba2ff9382a","tid":231773,"uid":25170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:07:15.000Z","msg":"lm <br />\n樓主全程大概用咗幾錢HKD?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下grad trip 睇下夠唔夠錢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1e1ed9cadf177fd1a00f8d12ce7b2f5da8f605","tid":231773,"uid":75439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a605c78a1e3e88237b07997095d518468d0d24","tid":231773,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:49:13.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"c00dfeb8fe733939424a7a5db698338c86f66899","tid":231773,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"黎緊都會去捷奧匈 留名<br />\nbtw Bratislava值唔值得停1日?"},{"pid":"c0be533f2dc3872ba02a5036fbf7aa568aa905d6","tid":231773,"uid":35821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T18:13:28.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6685f8f8d23ce63a7630d598465de34c91c902","tid":231773,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:30:03.000Z","msg":"斯洛伐克(Slovakia)<br />\n<br />\n係英國搭ryanair，兩個鐘就到左斯洛伐克首都bratislava<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。斯洛伐克和捷克以前係同一個國家，國名Czechoslovakia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，斯洛伐克於93年獨立。現在的斯洛伐克係歐盟成員國，用歐羅。<br />\n<br />\n係機場落左機，身上無歐羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，諗住機場一定有money exchange，點知無，好彩有一間便利店有賣車票，可以碌卡買車票。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K6M4279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6M4279.jpg&h=760873fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖from google<br />\n<br />\n斯洛伐克車票幾得意，係按你成個車程的時間嚟買票，如果車程係15分鐘以內，就買15分鐘的車票，車程係60分鐘以內，就買60分鐘的車票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，對唔識路的遊客都真係幾唔friendly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。上車要即時打票，唔打票就算你有票係手，都會當你係逃票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖from google<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YF6n346.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYF6n346.jpg&h=8b8612b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到hostel擺低野，識左個新加坡女仔就一齊出去食野+去free walking tour<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔講唔知，東歐其實好多free walking tour，去到一個特定地點等，會有人帶你短時間遊市中心的重要景點，再加講解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，完左隨心俾tips"},{"pid":"0e5f87003c50ede9964ed33ff59224d2e28cc590","tid":231773,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:30:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>斯洛伐克去左邊?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbratislava only"},{"pid":"eebf8e02707da40b7e6b48116b86d4fc7b8043ab","tid":231773,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔去克羅地亞呀？好正喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔夠時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9c62c3d4cfe2157c2dbc8a42223d4db991e451","tid":231773,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm <br />\n樓主全程大概用咗幾錢HKD?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下grad trip 睇下夠唔夠錢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三萬幾<br />\n無咩backpack經驗既話可以揀幾個國家集中去"},{"pid":"b32c346a15487d47b542cf46d4fde0c15d652876","tid":231773,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb6dc9f149de16cfdd781022911d5957ca0e0ea","tid":231773,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:35:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊都會去捷奧匈 留名<br />\nbtw Bratislava值唔值得停1日?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n值"},{"pid":"3f51bf63a8fcd29ca34c871ee241e1a4dab0a0c8","tid":231773,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:19:54.000Z","msg":"集合地點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p27bcW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp27bcW4.jpg&h=9d9961c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j9Fsv92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj9Fsv92.jpg&h=8d0bf719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面有個城堡，可以上去參觀同睇風景，我無去<br />\n<br />\n行入舊城區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22VgHM7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22VgHM7.jpg&h=ff32e992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係bratislava舊城區好多依D銅像，打卡位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bYRrb8A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbYRrb8A.jpg&h=65d09990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ym123q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ym123q.jpg&h=87504026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26M575u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26M575u.jpg&h=4552d45b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個警告牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n周圍見到好多飲水機<br />\n導遊話一年會有一日，人人都會上街慶祝，飲水機會出酒俾人狂歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n導遊又講佢地會慶祝name day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢地有個特別的calendar，傳統上每一個名都會有獨特的name day，連報紙都會寫今日係咩名的name day，果日算係第二個生日，當地人重視name day重多過生日，如果你個名唔係name day calendar上面，你就可以自己選一日做name day。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6UyY2oE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6UyY2oE.jpg&h=26beb785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成個舊城區有近300個皇冠圖案<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u5fHMh6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu5fHMh6.jpg&h=459df3d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19Ss9Of.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19Ss9Of.jpg&h=4ce786cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O85B5g7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO85B5g7.jpg&h=2497d7d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0J3457.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0J3457.jpg&h=94a61d5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U75t8Ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU75t8Ff.jpg&h=8e458b47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依間藍色教堂好靚，係當地人結婚的首選，早一年排都排唔到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行行下導遊又講，原來斯洛伐克人均月入只有800歐，如果要住市中心既屋，就算係最細既apartment，屋租都要人工既一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢問有冇人hometown既租金貴過依度，我勁想舉手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34d5dbc613b3971be16e6af351249c87893b07d","tid":231773,"uid":77363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:10:25.000Z","msg":"好睇lm 我都好鐘意東歐"},{"pid":"722f9db7f193fadd14091e64cd4f57a9f9c004f8","tid":231773,"uid":58081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:16:21.000Z","msg":"留明<br />\n月尾去"},{"pid":"ddfa416a8724ec46e0738d33c7be2ed3f9d6f5f7","tid":231773,"uid":75439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T02:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>lm <br />\n樓主全程大概用咗幾錢HKD?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下grad trip 睇下夠唔夠錢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三萬幾<br />\n無咩backpack經驗既話可以揀幾個國家集中去</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e180d890bf028707271bd4b5a4fd986887f54ac","tid":231773,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T03:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>lm <br />\n樓主全程大概用咗幾錢HKD?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下grad trip 睇下夠唔夠錢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三萬幾<br />\n無咩backpack經驗既話可以揀幾個國家集中去</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04270042f32e91792b4a14cab854a7c957bb4584","tid":231773,"uid":75439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T03:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>lm <br />\n樓主全程大概用咗幾錢HKD?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下grad trip 睇下夠唔夠錢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三萬幾<br />\n無咩backpack經驗既話可以揀幾個國家集中去</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10972ba13bff2db52d4ab2ee68a7320f5572c10","tid":231773,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:00:53.000Z","msg":"行完個tour跟左個新加坡女仔去同佢個當地朋友食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢個朋友勁靚女(btw無圖)，佢係旅遊局做野，成日出trip推廣斯洛伐克旅遊，有時都會接廣告嚟拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢推介我地食goat cheese dumplings<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為斯洛斯伐人很多都有畜牧綿羊，所以Goat cheese係斯洛斯伐菜有好重要的角色，傳統菜色多以goat cheese入菜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ow7H1jk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOw7H1jk.jpg&h=4ad3f4f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三款其實材料一樣，都係goat cheese+薯仔+面粉，紅色果款係辣的<br />\n唔太岩亞洲人口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zv2saD3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZv2saD3.jpg&h=9358f335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOnion soup好好飲，好似我地既酥皮湯，唔好以為好細份，個包大過我個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完野就返去訓，頭幾個國家留得比較短，第二日就去hungary首都budapest"},{"pid":"15f1dcc58e9221c8da9bd2b00dcdb79039e61a59","tid":231773,"uid":60550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}